      "recommendation": "Search for an Ohio or Wisconsin adult-life record naming Christiana Clark's maiden name or Berks County Pennsylvania birthplace — a death record, obituary, family Bible entry, widow's pension, or probate file from Green County WI or Coshocton County OH. A marriage record for Christiana (Schreck?) to William Clark would be most direct.",
